STATE of North Carolina
v.
Tavares REDD. No. 658P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 26, 2006. Tavares Redd, Pro Se. William Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, Clark Everett, District Attorney, for State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 21st day of November 2005 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Pitt County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 26th day of January 2006."
